{"tid":1215430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律小知識]良好市民被警察搜查時的應對","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:31:09.000Z","uid":65354,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5949546d8aca9f3c2237a53ad912f6308e54788a","tid":1215430,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JTurSi0LhJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJTurSi0LhJs&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=749c6a64\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JTurSi0LhJs</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除左基本資料外乜柒都唔好講 因為你有權唔答 <br />\n<br />\n然後就係問佢係咪要拘留 如果唔係拘留即係走得 佢警例232章54條嘅權力已經用完<br />\n</span></span><em><span style=\"color: pink;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(d) 扣留該人一段為作出該項搜查而合理需要的期間。</span></ins></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n如果佢唔係拘捕又唔肯放人，記得幫佢溫一溫警例 然後同佢上級/警察投訴課投訴佢唔熟讀警例</span></span>"},{"pid":"d5733acb0ffbc85cdd24a33b909031dc07bd95bf","tid":1215430,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cce1d9409f026dccc2ac5273243ea64bbe61288","tid":1215430,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd2b3fa1e1b47b027db0a6f534b1eab0c8e91fee","tid":1215430,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d27e768887b60bdac3fa69f78d0eed8011e80371","tid":1215430,"uid":55563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56077fc6891ea0e4fc6503f5a4f3cb5e7c15fa2e","tid":1215430,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce5a39